26.Virtual Dom : Don't  Rerender all the Dom just the part that want to change(React).
 Shadow Dom : Encapsulate complex elements in one element(Angular) or allows the encapsulation of smaller DOM elements and CSS styles into a single DOM element
 ex:<body><my-app></my-app> or <date-picker></date-picker> 
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/36012239/is-shadow-dom-fast-like-virtual-dom-in-react-js

